Package de.tum.in.tumcampus.activities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CafeteriaActivity
    Lists all dishes at selected cafeteria OPTIONAL: Const.CAFETERIA_ID set in incoming bundle (cafeteria to show)
    CalendarActivity
    Activity showing the user's calendar.
    ChatActivity
    Shows an ongoing chat conversation NEEDS: Const.CURRENT_CHAT_ROOM set in incoming bundle (json serialised object of class ChatRoom) Const.CURRENT_CHAT_MEMBER set in incoming bundle (json serialised object of class ChatMember)
    ChatRoomsSearchActivity
    This activity presents the chat rooms of user's lectures using the TUMOnline web service
    CurriculaActivity
    Activity to fetch and display the curricula of different study programs.
    CurriculaDetailsActivity
    Activity to display the curricula details of different programs.
    GradeChartActivity
    Displays charts generated with GradesActivity NEEDS: chartContent set in incoming bundle (html content to show)
    GradesActivity
    Activity to show the user's grades/exams passed.
    InformationActivity
    Provides information about this app and all contributors
    LecturesAppointmentsActivity
    This activity provides the appointment dates to a given lecture using the TUMOnline web service.
    LecturesDetailsActivity
    This Activity will show all details found on the TUMOnline web service identified by its lecture id (which has to be posted to this activity by bundle).
    LecturesPersonalActivity
    This activity presents the users' lectures using the TUMOnline web service the results can be filtered by the semester or all shown.
    MainActivity
    Main activity displaying the cards and providing navigation with navigation drawer
    NewsActivity
    Activity to show News (message, image, date)
    OpeningHoursDetailActivity
    An activity representing a single Item detail screen.
    OpeningHoursListActivity
    An activity representing a list of Items.
    OrganisationActivity
    Activity that shows the first level of organisations at TUM.
    OrganisationDetailsActivity
    Show all details that are available on TUMCampus to any organisation
    PersonsDetailsActivity
    Activity to show information about an person at TUM.
    PersonsSearchActivity
    Activity to search for employees.
    PlansActivity
    Activity to show plans.
    PlansDetailsActivity
    Activity to show plan details.
    RoomFinderActivity
    Activity to show a convenience interface for using the MyTUM room finder.
    RoomFinderDetailsActivity
    Displays the map regarding the searched room.
    SetupEduroamActivity
    Activity that allows the user to easily setup eduroam.
    StartupActivity
    Entrance point of the App.
    TransportationActivity
    Activity to show transport stations and departures
    TransportationDetailsActivity
    Activity to show transport departures for a specified station NEEDS: EXTRA_STATION set in incoming bundle (station name)
    TuitionFeesActivity
    Activity to show the user's tuition ; based on grades.java / quick solution
    UserPreferencesActivity
    Provides the preferences, encapsulated into an own activity.
